{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "To require grade 1 and 2 listed buildings to have a manned guard",
        "additional_details": "Evidence is that far too many historical buildings are being destroyed through fire and neglect. \r\nLiverpool has lost 3 buildings of historical significance in the past 2 years.",
        "background": "I propose that all grade 1 & 2 listed buildings are in a condition that a manned guard to be situated 24/7 365 days a year. This will prevent national treasures from being destroyed. The fabric and structure to be sound to allow a maned guard at all times to prevent damaging/fire",
